#

Pan-Seared New York Steak with Mushroom Risotto and Balsamic Reduction

$35
700 kcal

Allergens:

DairyMushrooms

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-ProteinLow-Carb

Tags:

SteakGourmetComfort Food

Description

A succulent pan-seared New York steak served with creamy mushroom risotto and a sweet balsamic reduction for a gourmet experience.

Ingredients

  • New York Strip Steak: 2 (8 oz) each
  • Olive Oil: 2 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
  • Shallot: 1, finely chopped
  • Garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • Arborio Rice: 1 cup
  • Chicken Broth: 4 cups
  • Parmesan Cheese: 1/2 cup, grated
  • Butter: 2 tbsp
  • Mushrooms: 1 cup, sliced
  • Balsamic Vinegar: 1/2 cup
